== SpamHammer

Hammer those spammers!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Features

* Punishment based on messages/time
* Punishment based on repeated messages
** Mute
** Kick
** Ban
* Unmute / Unban / Reset stats
* Permissions
** Bypass punishments
** Issue reset/unmute/reload

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Dependencies

* Bukkit 1.4.6 or later

